OL,3,CWelsh rugby boss warns it will take up
OL,4,Cto five years to be competitive again
OL,6,FOspreys CEO Lance Bradley has warned
OL,7,Fit could take up to five years for
OL,8,FWelsh rugby to be competitive again.
OL,10,FFor the better part of a decade, the
OL,11,Fsuccess of Wales' golden generation in
OL,12,Fthe Test arena glossed over the myriad
OL,13,Fof cracks which were appearing beneath
OL,14,Fthe top level.
OL,16,FThe game in Wales has been in a quiet
OL,17,Fdecline for years, with the four
OL,18,Fprofessional sides - Cardiff, Dragons,
OL,19,FOspreys and Scarlets - becoming less
OL,20,Fand less competitive.
