OL,3,CWelsh rugby boss warns it will take up
OL,4,Cto five years to be competitive again
OL,6,FIt will come as little surprise to
OL,7,Fthose who have been watching closely
OL,8,Fas budgets have been cut.
OL,10,FWales were whitewashed in this year's
OL,11,Fmen's Six Nations for the first time
OL,12,Fin 21 years and three of our regional
OL,13,Fsides finished in the bottom five of
OL,14,Fthe United Rugby Championship.
OL,16,FThe Ospreys were the team to provide a
OL,17,Fglimmer of hope domestically this year
OL,18,Fbut lost in the first round of the
OL,19,Fplay-offs last week.
