OL,3,CWelsh rugby boss warns it will take up
OL,4,Cto five years to be competitive again
OL,6,FIt took years for things to get this
OL,7,Fbad, and it'll take years to recover.
OL,8,FBut a plan is being drawn up with the
OL,9,FWRU and regions collaborating.
OL,11,F"There's undoubtedly challenges,"
OL,12,FBradley told ITV Cymru Wales.
OL,14,F"Some of the things that have happened
OL,15,Fin the past have been poor - some of
OL,16,Fthem very poor - but Abi (Tierney, WRU
OL,17,FCEO) and her new team are addressing
OL,18,Fthem.
