OL,3,CWelsh rugby boss warns it will take up
OL,4,Cto five years to be competitive again
OL,6,F"Some of it's difficult. Some of it
OL,7,Fwill take a while. But if you keep on
OL,8,Fdoing the same thing, you will keep on
OL,9,Fgetting the same result."
OL,11,FHe added: "What we're developing is a
OL,12,Ffive-year plan and by the end of that,
OL,13,Fwe would expect the clubs and the
OL,14,Fnational team to be properly
OL,15,Fcompetitive again.
OL,17,F"Could it happen earlier than that? Of
OL,18,Fcourse it could."
