OL,3,CWelsh rugby boss warns it will take up
OL,4,Cto five years to be competitive again
OL,6,FWhile Welsh rugby has been enduring
OL,7,Fits slow, painful decline - and we
OL,8,Fmight not have reached the nadir just
OL,9,Fyet with budgets for next season being
OL,10,Fcut back again - change has been
OL,11,Fpainfully hard to come by.
OL,13,FThe regions and WRU might currently be
OL,14,Fengaged in a review process but a
OL,15,Freport into the state of the game was
OL,16,Fmost recently commissioned just two
OL,17,Fyears ago. One of the recommendations
OL,18,Fin the infamous 'Oakwell Report' was a
OL,19,Freduction in the number of regions
OL,20,Ffrom four to three, to consolidate
OL,21,Flimited resources.
