OL,3,CWelsh rugby boss warns it will take up
OL,4,Cto five years to be competitive again
OL,6,FThat, of course, has not come to pass
OL,7,Fbut recently Nigel Walker, the WRU's
OL,8,Fexecutive director of rugby, refused
OL,9,Fto rule it out.
OL,11,FOver the years, the Ospreys have often
OL,12,Ffound themselves as the ones mooted to
OL,13,Fbecome extinct but it is not something
OL,14,FBradley is concerned about.
OL,16,FHe explained: "When you're conducting
OL,17,Fa thorough review - and all the clubs
OL,18,Fare involved in it - you can't start
OL,19,Fthat kind of review and say 'we're
OL,20,Fgoing to review everything but not
OL,21,Fthat'.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
