OL,3,CWelsh rugby boss warns it will take up
OL,4,Cto five years to be competitive again
OL,6,FBut that has come home to roost this
OL,7,Fyear and displayed itself in Wales'
OL,8,Fmiserable Six Nations campaign.
OL,10,F"It's really unusual to get
OL,11,Fsustainable success with a national
OL,12,Fteam unless you also have sustainable
OL,13,Fsuccess with your professional teams,"
OL,14,FBradley explained.
OL,16,FNot content with playing his role in
OL,17,Fsolving Welsh rugby's problems,
OL,18,FBradley is also taking on a project
OL,19,Fbespoke to his region.
