OL,3,CWelsh rugby boss warns it will take up
OL,4,Cto five years to be competitive again
OL,6,FHis first move when he came in as CEO
OL,7,Fearlier this year after spending five
OL,8,Fyears in charge of Gloucester Rugby
OL,9,Fwas to announce the Ospreys were
OL,10,Fmoving home.
OL,12,FThey currently play at the Swansea.com
OL,13,FStadium, which is owned by Swansea
OL,14,FCity Football Club. Facilities at the
OL,15,Fground are impressive, the pitch is
OL,16,Fperfect and hospitality offerings are
OL,17,Fplentiful.
OL,19,FBut the Ospreys come nowhere close to
OL,20,Ffilling the 20,000-seater stadium and
OL,21,Fmatchdays can feel soulless.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
