OL,3,CWelsh rugby boss warns it will take up
OL,4,Cto five years to be competitive again
OL,6,FSo now the region will set about
OL,7,Fredeveloping either the Brewery Field
OL,8,Fin Bridgend or St Helen's in Swansea.
OL,10,F"The business is in pretty good
OL,11,Fshape," Bradley explained. "But
OL,12,Fshackled by not having our own
OL,13,Fstadium. So before I joined, I spoke
OL,14,Fto the people at Y11, the ownership
OL,15,Fgroup, and asked a couple of things.
OL,17,F"One of them was 'are you serious
OL,18,Fabout getting your own stadium?
OL,19,FBecause I can pull some levers but
OL,20,Fthey all require a new stadium'.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
