OL,3,CWelsh rugby boss warns it will take up
OL,4,Cto five years to be competitive again
OL,6,F"I did feel strongly. The Swansea.com
OL,7,Fis a fabulous stadium. There are
OL,8,Fbeautiful facilities, a beautiful
OL,9,Fpitch, everything's great about it
OL,10,Fexcept that it's twice as big as we
OL,11,Fneed it to be.
OL,13,F"It's difficult to create an
OL,14,Fatmosphere at games in a 20,000-seat
OL,15,Fstadium. But also things like non-
OL,16,Fmatchday income, stadium sponsorship -
OL,17,Fnone of those things are possible when
OL,18,Fit's not not your own.
