OL,3,CWelsh rugby boss warns it will take up
OL,4,Cto five years to be competitive again
OL,6,F"You need to have somewhere where fans
OL,7,Fcan gather before a game and socialise
OL,8,Fwith each other and feel like they're
OL,9,Fpart of a rugby club and that's really
OL,10,Fhard to do in a big out-of-town
OL,11,Fstadium."
OL,13,FBradley admits the finances of a
OL,14,Fmultimillion-pound redevelopment of
OL,15,Feither ground are challenging but
OL,16,Finsists that the region's five-year
OL,17,Fplans are feasible.
